# Native rollup binaries are platform-pinned in optionalDependencies, so a
# locally-generated lockfile breaks CI on other platforms. We rely on bun.lock
# for reproducible bun installs and let `npm install` regenerate the lockfile
# fresh on each Node CI job.
package-lock.json

